==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Latticing
<hw>Lat"ti*cing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
act or process of making a lattice of, or of fitting a lattice
to.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bridge Building)</fld> <def>A system of bars
crossing in the middle to form braces between principal longitudinal
members, as of a strut.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Latus rectum</ent>⟦br⟧
